{"tid":1232180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【思想滲透工作】傳播臨時議會／政府嘅思想種子","createTime":"2019-06-16T14:46:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T01:09:55.000Z","uid":55449,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6575b76a099d72205eba8d1e91dd8dd0f15e135d","tid":1232180,"uid":55449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:46:56.000Z","msg":"多得林鄭猛烈助攻，挑起社會各界對港共政府嘅仇恨，<br />\n令到港九各界史無前例大團結，我哋好應食住個勢上，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撤回修例 -&gt; 釋放義士 -&gt; 平反正名 -&gt; 下台問責 -&gt; 黑警問罪 -&gt; 血債票償 -&gt; 真普選</span></span><br />\n<br />\n另外係時候要同步開展新一輪<span style=\"color: red;\">思想改造工作</span>，就係滲透「<span style=\"color: red;\">中共治下必亡</span>」嘅思想，<br />\n目標係要大部分香港人認同另立臨時議會並唔係政治禁忌，係<span style=\"color: red;\">香港最後唯一生路</span>，<br />\n呢樣工作要以溫水煮蛙方式進行，將「<span style=\"color: red;\">取而代之</span>」呢個概念念深埋喺潛意識入面，<br />\n同時間，<br />\n我哋要集思廣益，開始臨時憲法嘅編寫工作，<br />\n時機一旦配合就可以攞出嚟，配合臨時政府上場。<br />\n之前好似有人試過起草過獨立憲法，<br />\n<a href=\"https://sites.google.com/site/hkconstitution/home，\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsites.google.com%2Fsite%2Fhkconstitution%2Fhome%EF%BC%8C&d=xNvf4PJMmDX7L7bksShbPgZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=8446cb4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sites.google.com/site/hkconstitution/home，</a><br />\n大家一定要做好準備，唔可以白白浪費呢個百年難得一遇嘅機會。"},{"pid":"6a8c2f2b28e377b4f4676e16177fd5d408c77580","tid":1232180,"uid":42799,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:47:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1563290e9a66fa80434af270fd887cb5beb6d8cd","tid":1232180,"uid":231758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:50:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c034b5a355737dc144bf406d3094af8ce9bafa","tid":1232180,"uid":55449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:51:03.000Z","msg":"唔可以洩咗呢道氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f7e58b9f8e4a57a4ab614c3ba942d4116aae72d","tid":1232180,"uid":245310,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:58:23.000Z","msg":"第一步係要令全港市民認清呢個獨裁政府 得到絕大部份香港人支持<br />\n第二係比全世界知道冇任何野可以制衡現有政府 （黑警濫權 立法會比支那控制）<br />\n然後最重要係一定要有有權力同有錢嘅人企出黎建立臨時議會／政府<br />\n但好認真咁講 冇外國勢力真係好難可以達到呢一步<br />\n除非777又搞單大獲野出黎啦"},{"pid":"cffc0333987e1d2037391ffa3d5d929b70529625","tid":1232180,"uid":55449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:11:10.000Z","msg":"中共唔相信香港，亦都唔會對香港施以懷柔，<br />\n今次二百萬人已經證明香港係全球最大反共基地，<br />\n香港對於中共來講係一粒癌症毒瘤，會用盡一切手段打壓逼害，<br />\n所以唔使擔心未來冇大鑊嘢激發民心，<br />\n我哋而家要係底層做思想滲透，打好基礎，<br />\n千祈唔好依家即刻打正旗鼓獨立，無人會支持，<br />\n我哋依家要做嘅係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">思想滲透、思想滲透！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2CuUOCi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2CuUOCi.jpg&h=ed4b9659&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"98c5f9ba93503d14f0138adf84477ccd3cd1ba06","tid":1232180,"uid":55449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:40:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"919bef4bad222dc5b5b244366993388da650d6ff","tid":1232180,"uid":87985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:42:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b2b0718fa7b0c2763721f5844ac4e160dcd29689","tid":1232180,"uid":126256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:43:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9e4163e95fb39240b0ca109c55b264ad5ce963a","tid":1232180,"uid":259199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:41:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4315e48b2a05386181a39976a13eaf693c8a027a","tid":1232180,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T01:09:55.000Z","msg":"push"}]}